<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25340668">中国留学生向外国朋友批评中国社会问题，是正常的吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2318920" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">提问者已发现，原问题补充说明由于过于具体的情境描述，引起了很多误会和争议，故而删除。<br><br>原问题补充说明截屏保留见下，供参考。<br><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/bb21e3b4afb1703c7a4aff2872b3d502_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="478" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="//pic3.zhimg.com/bb21e3b4afb1703c7a4aff2872b3d502_r.jpg"></div>


</div>
